+ * with slop at least 1, the fragment:
+ * <pre>t1 t2 t1 t3 t2 t3</pre>
+ * matches twice:
+ * <pre>t1 t2 .. t3      </pre>
+ * <pre>      t1 .. t2 t3</pre>
